<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-full">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">How to apply for access to NPD data</h1>
    <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--xl  govuk-section-break--visible ">
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <div>
      <p class="govuk-!-font-size-16">
        From <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-education#content">Department for Education</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="govuk-inset-text">
      There's currently a 3 month lead time on processing applications
    </div>

    <p>We are working with the Office for National Statistics (ONS) to enable access to de-identified individual level data for research.</p>

    <p>For most applications, Department for Education (DfE) data will now be provided though the <a href="https://www.ons.gov.uk/aboutus/whatwedo/paidservices/virtualmicrodatalaboratoryvml">ONS Secure Research Service</a>.</p>

    <p>Access to the Secure Research Service may not be suitable if your request meets one or more of the following conditions:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Data is being processed to fulfil an essential public task (the data used is essential to run education and children’s services)</li>
      <li>You’re doing research funded by, commissioned by, or contracted to the DfE or other government departments and the Secure Research Service is not suitable</li>
      <li>You have approval from DfE before 1 June 2018, with agreement you would receive an extract, and the Secure Research Service is not suitable</li>
      <li>You want to re-use data already held by your requesting organisation and within the existing licence period</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">The application process</h2>

    <div id="step-by-step-navigation" class="app-step-nav app-step-nav--large app-step-nav--active" data-show-text="Show" data-hide-text="Hide" data-show-all-text="Show all" data-hide-all-text="Hide all">
      <div class="app-step-nav__controls">
        <!-- <button aria-expanded="false" class="app-step-nav__button app-step-nav__button--controls js-step-controls-button" aria-controls="step-panel-prepare-to-apply-1">Show all</button> -->
      </div>
      <ol class="app-step-nav__steps">
        <li class="app-step-nav__step js-step" id="check-youre-allowed-to-drive">
          <div class="app-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="1">
            <h2 class="app-step-nav__title">
              <span class="app-step-nav__circle app-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="app-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="app-step-nav__circle-background">
                    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Step</span> 1
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                <button class="app-step-nav__button app-step-nav__button--title js-step-title-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-panel-prepare-to-apply-1">
                  <span class="js-step-title-text">
                    Prepare to apply
                  </span>
                  <span class="app-step-nav__toggle-link js-toggle-link" aria-hidden="true">
                    Show
                  </span>
                </button>
              </span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="app-step-nav__panel js-panel js-hidden" id="step-panel-prepare-to-apply-1">
            <p class="app-step-nav__paragraph">You'll need to complete these steps before you can have access to the data.</p>

            <ol class="app-step-nav__list " data-length="3">
              <li class="app-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">
                <a data-position="1.1" class="app-step-nav__link js-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/request-copy-criminal-record" target="_blank">Get a basic DBS check</a>
              </li>
              <li class="app-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">
                <a data-position="1.2" class="app-step-nav__link js-link" href="https://www.ons.gov.uk/aboutus/whatwedo/statistics/requestingstatistics/approvedresearcherscheme" target="_blank">Register as an accredited researcher with the ONS</a>
              </li>
              <li class="app-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">
                <a data-position="1.3" class="app-step-nav__link js-link" href="https://www.ons.gov.uk/aboutus/whatwedo/paidservices/virtualmicrodatalaboratoryvml" target="_blank">Apply for access to the ONS Secure Research Service</a>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

        </li>

        <li class="app-step-nav__step js-step" id="explore-data">
          <div class="app-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="2">
            <h2 class="app-step-nav__title">
              <span class="app-step-nav__circle app-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="app-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="app-step-nav__circle-background">
                    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Step</span> 2
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                <button class="app-step-nav__button app-step-nav__button--title js-step-title-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-panel-explore-data-2">
                  <span class="js-step-title-text">
                    Find and explore data in the NPD
                  </span>
                  <span class="app-step-nav__toggle-link js-toggle-link" aria-hidden="true">
                    Show
                  </span>
                </button>
              </span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="app-step-nav__panel js-panel js-hidden" id="step-panel-explore-data-2">
            <p class="app-step-nav__paragraph">You can use this to find out more about the types of data held within the NPD.</p>
            <ol class="app-step-nav__list " data-length="3">
              <li class="app-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">
                <a data-position="1.2" class="app-step-nav__link js-link" href="/categories">Find variables and metadata</a>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

        </li>

        <li class="app-step-nav__step js-step" id="apply">
          <div class="app-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="3">
            <h2 class="app-step-nav__title">
              <span class="app-step-nav__circle app-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="app-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="app-step-nav__circle-background">
                    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Step</span> 3
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                <button class="app-step-nav__button app-step-nav__button--title js-step-title-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-panel-apply-3">
                  <span class="js-step-title-text">
                    New or existing applications
                  </span>
                  <span class="app-step-nav__toggle-link js-toggle-link" aria-hidden="true">
                    Show
                  </span>
                </button>
              </span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="app-step-nav__panel js-panel js-hidden" id="step-panel-apply-3">
            <div class="govuk-inset-text govuk-!-margin-top-0">
              <p>If you have an application in process and have any questions, please email us at <a href="mailto:data.sharing@education.gov.uk">data.sharing@education.gov.uk</a> and we’ll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
            </div>

            <p>When you are ready to make an application, please contact <a href="mailto:data.sharing@education.gov.uk">data.sharing@education.gov.uk</a> and we’ll:</p>

            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
              <li>send you an <strong>application form</strong> and <strong>guidance</strong> to complete it – including the new  method for classifying data identification risk and sensitivity levels</li>
              <li>help you through the Data Sharing Approval Panel (<abbr title="Data Sharing Approval Panel">DSAP</abbr>) approval process</li>
              <li>provide the final agreement and declaration for you to sign</li>
            </ul>

          </div>

        </li>

        <li class="app-step-nav__step js-step" id="application-review">
          <div class="app-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="4">
            <h2 class="app-step-nav__title">
              <span class="app-step-nav__circle app-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="app-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="app-step-nav__circle-background">
                    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Step</span> 4
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                <button class="app-step-nav__button app-step-nav__button--title js-step-title-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-panel-application-review-5">
                  <span class="js-step-title-text">
                    Application review
                  </span>
                  <span class="app-step-nav__toggle-link js-toggle-link" aria-hidden="true">
                    Show
                  </span>
                </button>
              </span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="app-step-nav__panel js-panel js-hidden" id="step-panel-application-review-5">
            <p class="app-step-nav__paragraph">Your application will need to be reviewed by the DSAP panel before a decision can be made.</p>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">What is DSAP?</h3>
            <p class="app-step-nav__paragraph">The Data Sharing Approval Panel (DSAP) is a Departmental group consisting of members of staff from across the Department. DSAP supports the Department in fulfilling its duties by reviewing and deciding whether to approve applications for access to personal identifiable data.</p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="app-step-nav__step js-step" id="application-approved">
          <div class="app-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="5">
            <h2 class="app-step-nav__title">
              <span class="app-step-nav__circle app-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="app-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="app-step-nav__circle-background">
                    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Step</span> 5
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                <button class="app-step-nav__button app-step-nav__button--title js-step-title-button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="step-panel-application-approved-5">
                  <span class="js-step-title-text">
                    Application approved
                  </span>
                  <span class="app-step-nav__toggle-link js-toggle-link" aria-hidden="true">
                    Show
                  </span>
                </button>
              </span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="app-step-nav__panel js-panel js-hidden" id="step-panel-application-approved-5">
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Application approved?</h3>
            <p class="app-step-nav__paragraph">You'll be sent an email detailing what to do next.</p>

            <h2 class="govuk-heading-s">Accessing the data using the Secure Research Service</h2>

            <p>Once you are an ONS approved researcher and your data application has been approved, there are 2 ways you can access DfE data for approved projects through the Secure Research Service. You can use:</p>
            <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
              <li><strong>Physical labs</strong> – you can book a session to access DfE data at 1 of 5 ONS locations across the UK
                <li><strong>Remote access</strong> – once your organisation meets security standards and have organised connectivity with ONS, you can access data online using your own equipment subject to specified conditions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>For more details on how to become approved for remote access, please contact <a href="mailto:research.support@ons.gov.uk">research.support@ons.gov.uk</a></p>

            <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--l  govuk-section-break--visible ">

            <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Application denied?</h3>
            <p class="app-step-nav__paragraph">If your application has been denied then you will be contacted to discuss the reasons why.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions or queries regarding the data or the process of applying please get in touch with us at <a href="mailto:data.sharing@education.gov.uk">data.sharing@education.gov.uk</a></p>
  </div>

